    public interface StubIndexExtension<Key,Psi extends PsiElement>
    Definition of the index. Implement the ObjectStubSerializer.indexStub(Stub, IndexSink)) function in your language's Stub Elements to fill the index with data.
    See Also:
    ObjectStubSerializer.indexStub(Stub, IndexSink)}
